Description: Core5 Studio was founded with one main focus: Fix everything wrong in the fitness industry. With our years of experience working.
Headquarters Regions: Tampa Bay Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Core5 Studio was founded with one main focus: Fix everything wrong in the fitness industry. With our years of experience working with hundreds of different health clubs and studios nation wide; we learned what clients loved and, more importantly, what they hated. A personalized approach that encompasses the true community feel people are looking for has not ever existed in the way that Core5 has instilled it in Brandon FL. Our hybrid approach blends an even balance of the 5 fundamentals of fitness: Strength Training, Cardiovascular Endurance, Flexibility, Nutrition, and SUPPORT. We specialize in High Intensity Interval Training, Yoga/Hot Yoga, Pilates Reformer Training, Spin/Cycle, Ballet Barre and One on One Personal Training. Think of the incredible results you see from Orange Theory and P90X refined by the personalization and attention to detail you can only find in a high end yoga studio. All of this, with no hidden fees and no contracts. With these principles in place, our no nonsense just "Fitness to the Core" mantra was born. The health and fitness industry is riddled with horror stories from consumers paying for results and receiving none. The unfortunate reality is, they suffer by default because the industry is designed to capitalize on their ignorance. Core5 Studio sheds light on the path to their goals. In a traditional health club, trainers and group instructors naturally work against one another. Trainers are only compensated when they are in a session with a client while instructors are only compensated based on class participation. Neither benefits from the idea of synergy. Neither bothers to recommend the other's services and the only person suffering is the client. While this issue plagues the industry, at Core5 we have put together a model that THRIVES off of that synergy. Our client's overall health and results are the only focus. Our staff strive to bridge the gap for every client, in every session. Just show up and we take care of the rest.

Description: Vincent Celentano INC is an investment consulting company helping entrepreneurs to obtain funding for their investment plans
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: In July 1998, in cooperation with the Micra International Development, Vincent Celentano INC was established as the first investing company dealing with investments fund for Eastern Europe in order to provide capital for expansion of a vital part of the new independent European economies which grew slowly in those years. At that time share capital and other venture capital for Vincent Celentano INC at manta were almost non-existent, and even loans from commercial banks were rare, generally with very high interest rates and guarantee conditions. However, despite the unpleasant environment for Vincent Celentano INC, in 1997, small businesses accounted for 34% of total employment in those markets and 37% of national GDP. Recognizing the potential for development of the private sector, Vincent Celentano INC was established as the first mover of speculative capital. The following years caused the unstable political and economic climate. Despite the seriousness of the situation, companies with portfolio Vincent Celentano INC continued their work, and in some cases even increased their capital. Also, the professional team of Vincent Celentano INC was constantly supporting its companies and continuing investments with high growth potential. At the time of these significant challenges, the results of Vincent Celentano INC were outstanding, and at that time Vincent Celentano INC funded manta companies amounted to 3% of GDP European market. From 1998 to 2004, Vincent Celentano INC invested in 34 companies from 34 separate industries, including leading newspaper, wireless internet provider and manufacturer of equipment for heating, ventilation and air conditioning. The benefits of investment from Vincent Celentano INC were diverted to the small investment fund managed by Vincent Celentano INC local office of the Center for Entrepreneurship and Executive Development, as well as contribute to the other regional funds. In October 2005, Vincent Celentano started Vincent Celentano Capital Market to provide long-term equity and quasi-equity capital to small and medium enterprises. While the global financial situation gradually started to calm after the political and economic crisis, some received little foreign investment and small businesses lacked basic finance needful to expand. Recognizing the need for a strong private sector in order to stabilize the regional economy, Vincent Celentano Capital Market through its local team to provide sustainable funding and technical assistance to local businesses. Vincent Celentano Capital Market aimed to build unity between these neighboring countries through economic partnerships, working with the understanding that economic prosperity can lead to greater cooperation. Vincent Celentano Capital Market has identified and supported joint ventures working overseas, as well as those using the Vincent Celentano Capital Market were able to adopt Western management practices. Vincent Celentano Capital Market portfolio includes supermarket chain, company logistics services company system integrator, distributor of IT equipment and factoring company. Today, Vincent Celentano INC is fully invested and no longer requires active investment opportunities.

Headquarters Regions: Greater Detroit Area, Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: HealthKibo is building a platform to build a community-driven health recommendations engine helping people optimize their health, access to an intelligent search engine to find cheaper medications, and tools to help people remember to take their medications.  The first solution is an intelligent search engine to help identify possible ways to substitute medications when cheaper non-inferior ones are available. This search combines therapeutic equivalence with pricing information. This is particularly useful for patients who may be on a brand name and unaware of a therapeutic equivalent. Patients can save their medications and receive alerts when prices change hopefully keeping the affect on their pocket a minimum.  Secondly, they offer an evidence backed recommendation engine which helps patients identify what medications they should be on based on their health conditions, gender, and age. This is novel (at least at the consumer level). This can be used to make sure patients are taking the what the most recent research recommends. This can help the average person figure what medications they should be taking which can sometimes be left of off their medication regimen in the process of trying to navigate the confusing health care system we partake in.  Thirdly, they offer a comprehensive reminder system.  They offer reminders through SMS, phone calls, email, and IM (MSN, Yahoo, GTalk, etc.). The service is available to the international community though local numbers in over 100 countries and offer two way communication. Offering local numbers makes it easy for people in their respective countries to respond without incurring high costs. THey offer ways to track medication and also offer proxy monitoring. So, a third party can be notified if a patient or family member or care taker misses a dose.  HealthKibo use to be previously known as DrugBin.
